data.description:
Looking for a nearly-new home brimming with potential? Your search ends here! This immaculate home, built just one year ago by its current owners, is now available and offers incredible possibilities.

Highlights:
2 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 2 car garage, flex room , main floor laundry, unfinished walkout lower level, large windows with scenic views of pond that backs property, and an inviting walking trail that encircles the entire neighborhood! 

One of the standout features of this property is its walk-out lower level, presenting an exciting opportunity to unleash your creativity and build equity. Imagine additional bedrooms, an extra bathroom, a cozy family room, or even the home theatre you've always dreamed of.

Nestled in a vibrant community, this home offers more than just a living space; it provides a lifestyle. Close proximity to breweries, grocery stores, and plenty of shopping options. Potential for 2.75% assumable mortgage for qualified VA buyer.
